  "body": "When the indexing service doesn't yet know anything, `/eth/syncing?backend=l2` returns `{\"syncing\":true,\"highestKnownTransactionIndex\":-1,\"currentTransactionIndex\":0}` which rollup/client.go attempts to parse into a SyncStatus so rollup/sync_service.go can check `status.Syncing`... only `json: cannot unmarshal number -1 into Go struct field SyncStatus.highestKnownTransactionIndex of type uint64`. (FWIW, the core reason I was actually seeing this was because I should have been using `--rollup.backend l1` instead of `l2`, but clearly the schema is wrong.)",
